Titles.jpn: 美少女戦士セーラームーンSuperS セーラー９戦士集結！ブラック・ドリーム・ホールの奇跡

Summaries.eng: After the arrival of a mysterious boy named Peruru, Tokyo’s children, including Chibiusa, begin sleepwalking out of their homes! Sailor Moon and the other sailors must now fight to save the children before the enemy places the entire world into an eternal sleep!

Aliases: Sailor Moon SuperS: The Movie: Black Dream Hole
Pretty Soldier Sailor Moon SuperS: The Nine Sailor Soldiers Unite! Miracle of the Black Dream Hole
